text:
For reference, I used to live near the hotel...Casa Cipriani brings with it a wonderful energy and vibrancy that Southern Manhattan needed back. The decor as you'd expect is stunning, the service stellar and the views in every direction will take your breath away. The hotel is right on the water + it literally feels like you are sailing on the most well appointed cruise liner from a different era. Breakfast or lunch on the terrace is a must do whether you are a guest or a member. You feel like you are walking onto the chicest of movie sets for cocktails + dinner at the Pickering Bar. Casa also have a state of the art spa + fitness center for members + hotel guests.

Pack a bag + journey on with me,
@MichaelaGuzy
